OL,4,CKPMG's 16,000 UK staff to get more time
OL,5,Coff work
OL,6, KPMG has told its 16,000 staff they can
OL,7, leave early one day a week as part of a
OL,8, move towards more flexible working
OL,9, after lockdown.
OL,11,FThe accountancy giant said staff will
OL,12,Fwork in KPMG offices for four days each
OL,13,Ffortnight, with the rest of their
OL,14,Fworking week at home and client sites.
OL,16,FStaff will also get an extra
OL,17,Ftwo-and-a-half-hours off per week over
OL,18,Fthe summer "to promote wellbeing".
OL,20,FKPMG's move is another example of big
OL,21,Ffirms overhauling home-office life.
